{"tid":749461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母成日鳩噏當秘笈","createTime":"2018-07-20T04:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T09:26:59.000Z","uid":79651,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c972bf19e56a500b2e8fd7e6574fdcb2a1bec42","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"小學嘅時候唔鍾意刷牙所以蛀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老母話：「蛀咗就算喇，啲牙遲啲會甩晒之後生過啲新嘅牙，到時要好好保養喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我大個先知⋯ 大牙係唔會甩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後蛀到要杜牙根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家提返起件事，我老母話鳩我天真咁都信，應該自己查證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ac4fc98e1ae107d423f5e2810cc2b090e23f1b","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd8a2e475fc9c4d90bf8ea5aece65146fad19539","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"有無人老母都係咁"},{"pid":"00e16c0071a571fd72159afc97abe0dbd50edeb3","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"入嚟分享吓"},{"pid":"a7b34c4cb4e4f4385e49e64af4a72243e2245477","tid":749461,"uid":71619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"你肯定係親生？"},{"pid":"a87a147d0906579a8e792b719d9a876c007337ac","tid":749461,"uid":159734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8183ad3557f097cd7647af85d20435b1727c9542","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"無人分享？咁我繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1269f8da17c5719148de022ed52caabf4d1cefb8","tid":749461,"uid":79651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"細個嘅時候老豆老母帶我去體育館打羽毛球，<br />\n我老母指住啲未降落嚟嘅籃球架(7-8米高？)同我講：「睇吓啲籃球架幾高，打籃球嗰啲人就係去到咁高打架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我好似小一？我信撚咗 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}